## Writing Up & Presenting Results



<div class='question-begin'>Question 9</div><div class='question-body'>



Provide key model results in a formatted table.

:::{.callout-tip appearance="simple" collapse="true"}

### Hint 

Use `tab_model()` from the __sjPlot__ package. For a quick guide, review the [tables flashcard](https://uoepsy.github.io/dapr2/2526/labs/1_b3_reading.html#tables).

:::



</div><p class="question-end"></p>





<div style="display:none;">




::: {#tbl-dass-modresults .cell layout-align="center" tbl-cap='Regression table for DASS-21 model'}

